To install erCv :
   mkdir build
   cd build
   cmake ..
   make

if you want to change c++ compiler :
   change cmake .. by cmake -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=/usr/bin/c++_compiler ..

if you don't want to build python library :
   tell cmake -DBUILD_PYTHON_MODULE=OFF ..

For any trouble please contact:
    edward.romero@univ-orleans.fr and pray that it 's still ok
    or 
    cyril.bordreuil@univ-montp2.fr